root: ^You're here! I'm so glad you could make it.
^Welcome to your first day at the Early Bird cafe!
^There's always lots to do, but for now why don't you start by stocking the counters with pastries?
^Its pretty simple, just use your MOUSE to drop items into their appropriate windows based on the signs in front of them.
^I'm sure you'll do great. Good luck with your first day!
